Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- You should have seen\Nthe look on Joanna's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she'd ever\Nlost a fight before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, not fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough crowd tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess Ironwood should have paid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for better cell block entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And he smiles. Did I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, it's your game.\NI don't make the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry, for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a deal with the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and he paid the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all happening so fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but Clover wouldn't let up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have worked against\NTyrian if Clover just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing that really stings,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time in a\Nwhile, I thought maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I could be around somebody. Anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my semblance\Nmaking it complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it just feels like\Na childish dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Believe it or not, I know\Na little of what that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When people are worried\Nyou're gonna sniff out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,their secrets, they tend to push you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes a real connection(barrier\Nbuzzing) difficult.
