Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't get to keep that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- You keep saying that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was your weapon\Ncovered in his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] If you really want
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to know what happened\Nmohawk, why not open the cell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- If I open this cell, it\Nwon't be to shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. Because you don't\Ncare about the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want someone to be mad at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier than taking an honest\Nlook at what side you're on.
